name: slimey
description:
im so excited to put out this sister piece for whatever loser! im really enjoying this theme of shiny glittery backgrounds, like a collectors edition card! i am so thankful to be able to draw so much inspiration from friends in such a short amount of time within meeting them.

thank you so much to all my friends and followers who support me and cheer me on despite life getting in the way. it means more than you know!
